{
  "chapter": "017",
  "title": "汉兴以来诸侯王年表",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "古代封建。"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>代以前的分封情况太久远了。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>代分封采用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五等</span>爵位：<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伯</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">子</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">男</span>。"
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "然而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯禽</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>，封地各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四百里</span>，这是亲近亲属的道义，也是表彰有德之人；又把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太公</span>封在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，兼有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五侯</span>的土地，这是尊崇勤劳功臣。"
    },
    "1.4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成</span>王、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康</span>王所分封的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百</span>个诸侯中，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">同姓</span>诸侯有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十五</span>个，封地大的不超过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>，小的只有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十里</span>，用来辅佐护卫<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王室</span>。"
    },
    "1.5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑</span>等国，或超出或减损规模。"
    },
    "1.6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">厉</span>王、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">幽</span>王以后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王室</span>衰微，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侯伯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">彊国</span>兴起，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>势弱，已无力匡正天下。这并非<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>行不够纯正，而是形势所迫而已。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "汉初分封。"
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起，确定了王侯两等爵位。"
    },
    "2.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>末年，不是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>却称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的，没有战功而上面不想封却当了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侯</span>的，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>共同<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>讨他。"
    },
    "2.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子弟</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">同姓</span>封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九国</span>，只有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">长沙</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">异姓</span>；而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>封<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侯</span>的则有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百有馀人</span>。"
    },
    "2.4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span>以东到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽阳</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>的封国；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>以南，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大行</span>山左转，越过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阿</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甄</span>以东逼近海边，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>的封国；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>以西，向南到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九疑</span>，东面环绕<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">穀</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>，靠近<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">长沙</span>的封国：这些国家外面都接邻<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>之地。"
    },
    "2.5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "而内地北面以山以东的地区全都是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的地盘，大的诸侯国或占<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五六郡</span>，连城<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十</span>座，设置百官宫观，僭越有如<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。"
    },
    "2.6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝中央只拥有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东郡</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江陵</span>以西至<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>，北面从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云中</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇西</span>，加上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">内史</span>总共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十五郡</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>又颇有在这些郡中享有食邑的。"
    },
    "2.7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "为什么会这样呢？<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>初定之时，皇家的骨肉同姓尚少，所以要广封<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶孽</span>使其强大，用以镇抚四海，以此护卫<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "推恩分封。"
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝安定<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百年（时长）</span>间，亲属关系日渐疏远，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>中有些人骄奢淫逸，惯于听<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">邪臣</span>的谋划而行淫乱之事，严重的甚至叛逆，轻微的也不守<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>度，以致危及性命，身死国灭。"
    },
    "3.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>借鉴上古做法，于是加以恩惠，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>得以行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">推恩</span>之制，把国邑分给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子弟</span>。于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>分为七国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>分为六国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>分为五国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>分为三国，还有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的支<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶子</span>被封为王，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王子</span>的支庶被封为侯，共有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百有馀</span>人。"
    },
    "3.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>叛乱之时，先后有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>因故被削地，于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>没有了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北边</span>的郡，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">长沙</span>没有了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南边</span>的郡，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的支郡以及名山陂海全都收归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝。"
    },
    "3.4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>势力渐渐衰微，大国不过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀城</span>，小侯不过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十里</span>，对上足以供奉贡赋职责，对下足以供养<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">祭祀</span>之需，以此作为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>的藩屏辅佐。"
    },
    "3.5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝直辖的郡有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八九十</span>个，形状交错在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之间，犬牙交错，掌握着险要关塞的地利，造成了根本强盛、枝叶削弱的形势，尊卑分明，万事各得其所。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "结语。"
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">迁</span>谨慎地记录<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>以来至<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">太初</span>年间的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，排列他们增减的时代，使后世得以查览。"
    },
    "4.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "形势虽强，归根到底要以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>为根本。"
    }
  }
}